nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 199 is the 177th issue of Star Wars Insider magazine and the 107th issue published by Titan Magazines. It was published on December 15, 2020. It contains the first published media from Star Wars: The High Republic, "Starlight: Part One - Go Together," written by Charles Soule.

Fiction is back! Star War Insider #199 features the first in an ongoing series of Star Wars: The High Republic stories, exclusive to the magazine! The first is by acclaimed Star Wars author Charles Soule – a prequel to his Star Wars: The High Republic novel!
